* Choose release name:
  - a bar for micro version
  - a restaurant for minor version
* Check for milestone bugs
* Edit NEWS and add the tickets fixed for this milestone; for example:
  https://core.fluendo.com/trac/cgi-bin/trac.cgi/report/16?format=tab&MILESTONE=0.1.2
* bump nano in configure.ac
* edit ChangeLog and add === release 0.1.2 ===
* commit to SVN
* create release tag:
  svn cp https://svn.fluendo.com/svn/flumotion/trunk https://svn.fluendo.com/svn/flumotion/tags/flumotion-0.1.2
* fix up ticket list to do and milestone  
* add news entry on site
* send out mail
